---
// Brief About Teaser section
import SectionHeader from '../SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section class="relative py-32 sm:py-40 lg:py-48 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] ambient-blob bg-gold-400"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] ambient-blob-navy"></div>

  <div class="section-inner max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 relative z-10">
    <SectionHeader label="About Us" labelHy="&#1348;&#1381;&#1408; &#1396;&#1377;&#1405;&#1387;&#1398;" labelRu="О нас" labelFr="À propos" labelAr="من نحن" />

    <h2 class="gs-reveal font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[3.5rem] text-text-primary font-semibold mb-10 leading-[1.1]">
      <span data-i18n data-hy="&#1355;&#1387;&#1399;&#1407; &#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1408;&#1377;&#1412;&#1377;&#1398;&#1401;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1408;<br /><span class='text-gold-gradient'>&#1350;&#1381;&#1408;&#1380;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1352;&#1408;&#1400;&#1399;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;</span>" data-en="Precision in Every<br /><span class='text-gold-gradient'>Investment Decision</span>" data-ru="Точность в каждом<br /><span class='text-gold-gradient'>инвестиционном решении</span>" data-fr="Précision dans chaque<br /><span class='text-gold-gradient'>décision d'investissement</span>" data-ar="دقة في كل<br /><span class='text-gold-gradient'>قرار استثماري</span>">Precision in Every<br /><span class="text-gold-gradient">Investment Decision</span></span>
    </h2>

    <div class="gs-reveal max-w-[720px]">
      <p class="text-[17px] text-card-body font-light leading-[1.75] tracking-[0.01em]" data-i18n data-hy="ALGOSPHERE ASSET MANAGEMENT &#1384;&#1398;&#1391;&#1381;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1385;&#1397;&#1400;&#1410;&#1398;&#1384; &#1396;&#1377;&#1405;&#1398;&#1377;&#1379;&#1387;&#1407;&#1377;&#1409;&#1390; &#1383; &#1411;&#1377;&#1391;, &#1400;&#1401; &#1392;&#1408;&#1377;&#1402;&#1377;&#1408;&#1377;&#1391;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1398;&#1381;&#1408;&#1380;&#1408;&#1400;&#1410;&#1396;&#1377;&#1397;&#1387;&#1398; &#1411;&#1400;&#1398;&#1380;&#1381;&#1408;&#1387; &#1391;&#1377;&#1404;&#1377;&#1406;&#1377;&#1408;&#1396;&#1377;&#1398; &#1396;&#1381;&#1403;&#1417;" data-en="Algosphere Asset Management enters Armenia's rapidly growing capital markets at an inflection point. With mathematical precision and deep local expertise, we manage closed-end investment funds for discerning investors who seek disciplined, transparent, and long-term value creation." data-ru="Algosphere Asset Management выходит на стремительно растущий рынок капитала Армении в поворотный момент. Математическая точность и глубокое знание местного рынка — основа нашего управления закрытыми инвестиционными фондами для инвесторов, ценящих дисциплину, прозрачность и долгосрочный рост." data-fr="Algosphere Asset Management investit les marchés de capitaux arméniens en plein essor, à un tournant décisif. Précision mathématique et expertise locale approfondie guident notre gestion de fonds fermés, au service d'investisseurs exigeants qui privilégient discipline, transparence et création de valeur durable." data-ar="تدخل Algosphere Asset Management أسواق رأس المال الأرمنية سريعة النمو في نقطة تحول. بدقة رياضية وخبرة محلية عميقة، نحن ندير صناديق استثمار مغلقة للمستثمرين المميزين الذين يسعون لخلق قيمة منضبطة وشفافة وطويلة الأجل.">
        Algosphere Asset Management enters Armenia's rapidly growing capital markets at an inflection point. With mathematical precision and deep local expertise, we manage closed-end investment funds for discerning investors who seek disciplined, transparent, and long-term value creation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Learn More link hidden - single page mode -->
  </div>
</section>
